name: Fifuli Remastered
description:
Controls : 

Move and click with mouse to control Drawing,

Press key : 
1,2,3,4,5 to change render layers. 
C : Randomize all.
b : Clean Background. 

This is the generative system that i first made for my node.js app.The node.js version works with multiple users. Watch that one here : 
https://fifuli2.herokuapp.com/

THIS is a stand alone version(NOT MULTI USER) that has been modified to work in hen BUT it has shaders that you can trigger using the numbers. 

Wait for it to load(it will eventually load, trust me) or watch it in this external link :
https://mmtt.com.ar/jpupper/nftsapps/fifuliremastered/

Is better in fullscreen always

This generative system is kind of messy but it allows you to do very different and complex drawings.
